Introduction

Suhyeon is a South Korean singer; dancer, and actress under MYSTIC Story. She is a member of the girl group Billlie.

In 2016, she was a contestant on MNET' survival show Produce 101 where she was eliminated in episode 5 after ranking 69th place.

In 2017, Suhyeon became a contestant on the survival show MIXNINE, where she was eliminated in the final episode. In the same year, she made her acting debut in the drama "Girls' Generation 1979".

She was a member of the trainee group Mystic Rookies, who later became Billlie, with whom she made her debut on November 10, 2021 with the release of the mini album "The Billage of Perception : Chapter One".

On June 15, 2023, it was revelead that Suhyeon would go on a hiatus due to health issues. On April 12, 2024, MYSTIC Story announced that her hiatus was over and that she would be coming back to the group.
